Interface LinkedListInterface<E>

Type Parameters:
E - The type of elements to be stored in the linked list.
All Known Implementing Classes:
Course, DoublyLinkedList, Term
public interface LinkedListInterface<E>
The LinkedListInterface is an interface representing a generic linked list data structure.
